- *
- *   -> PRLI to FCID of that PWWN (PRLI timeout 2 * R_A_TOV)
- *    -> ABTS if timeout (ABTS tomeout - 2 * R_A_TOV)
- *                        <- PRLI response
- *    -> Retry PRLI. Num retries using vnic.cfg
- *
- */
